<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-290-070  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 290 070.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacUser  May 1990 v6 n5 p42(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>FlexForm Business Templates. (Software Review) (Antic SoftwareFlexForm Business Templates forms-design package) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Wiggins, Robert R.andM;</AUTHOR><SUMMARY>Antic Software Inc's FlexForm Business Templates is a set ofpre-designed forms created in SmartForm Designer.andP;  The packagecomes in two volumes which sell for $89.95 each: Volume I's 46templates include forms for inventory, production, selling,billing, collections, envelopes, and delivery, while Volume II hasforms for purchasing, receiving, accounting, disbursing, payroll,and miscellaneous forms.andP;  Users can work with the formsimmediately using the bundled SmartForm Assistant program ormodify them with a full version of SmartForm Designer.andP;  Thetemplates are excellent and are designed to work well withhigh-quality output devices.andM;</SUMMARY><DESCRIPT>Company:   Antic Software (products).andO;Product:   FlexForm Business Templates (Computer program).andO;Topic:     Forms ManagementSoftware packagesEvaluation.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>FlexForm Business TemplatesandM;FlexForm's templates are intended to free you from having to design your ownforms.andP;  You can just see these forms, created by the FORMula team ofinformation specialists, as they come, using the supplied SmartForm Assistantprogram, or you can purchase SmartForm Designer and modify them.andP;  (See &quot;InGood Form,&quot; January '90 for more information on forms-design software.)andM;FlexForm Business Templates: General Business, Volume I consists of 46templates, including forms for inventory, production, selling delivery,billing, collections, and envelopes.andP;  Volume II includes purchasing,receiving, accounting, employee/payroll, disbursing, and envelope forms, andmiscellaneous forms such as a faxtransmital sheet.andM;These templates are very good, designed to work with high-quality outputdevices such as the LaserWriter while remaining attractive on ImageWriters.andM;One caveat: Be sure you're buying the General Business templates, becauseAntic has another line that is also called FlexForm Business Templates, whichis a line of PageMaker templates.andM;Antic Software, 544 Second St., San Francisco, CA 94107; (415) 957-0886.andO;$89.95 per volume.andO;</TEXT></DOC>